{"tid":326551,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"天涯明月刀ol 新航海時代","createTime":"2017-07-18T05:46:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-19T08:00:14.000Z","uid":57044,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9ed4f7843839e9aee11bba55a6e91236d37f9769","tid":326551,"uid":57044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:46:39.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打一齊玩？我玩緊新ser 蒼海雲帆-青龍永夜<br />\n<br />\n升到85lv 可以造船，五個人坐一隻船，一人掌舵，其他人控炮，滅火。<br />\n<br />\n航海跑商，好似巨商咁買賣貨物，我暫時升到36lv，有巴打玩的話留言一齊出海。"},{"pid":"bd8d751b156ec3c3127ea39c5167cb61c337bd09","tid":326551,"uid":10284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:56:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇巴打一齊玩？我玩緊新ser 蒼海雲帆-青龍永夜<br />\n<br />\n升到85lv 可以造船，五個人坐一隻船，一人掌舵，其他人控炮，滅火。<br />\n<br />\n航海跑商，好似巨商咁買賣貨物，我暫時升到36lv，有巴打玩的話留言一齊出海。</blockquote><br />\n好似好正咁喎"},{"pid":"a7209ed354130da8ce52227df3921d00ce1e5a80","tid":326551,"uid":57044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T06:06:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇巴打一齊玩？我玩緊新ser 蒼海雲帆-青龍永夜<br />\n<br />\n升到85lv 可以造船，五個人坐一隻船，一人掌舵，其他人控炮，滅火。<br />\n<br />\n航海跑商，好似巨商咁買賣貨物，我暫時升到36lv，有巴打玩的話留言一齊出海。</blockquote><br />\n好似好正咁喎</blockquote><br />\n畫面同控制都好正。但係大陸game，一定係pay to win，心態上意識到呢樣野就好開心。<br />\n<br />\n打下劇情，跑商，殺人幾好玩，唔錯。<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/18/140606_9e5493906183d570c09452b8ed94bb38.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F18%2F140606_9e5493906183d570c09452b8ed94bb38.jpg&h=9fb01dcb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/18/140608_da7d40fc3d1d4a326499450577842511.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F18%2F140608_da7d40fc3d1d4a326499450577842511.jpg&h=c1f04b09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPicture from google."},{"pid":"e01eb37b6030c56a1756501134832ffb2a166e7f","tid":326551,"uid":63888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T06:20:45.000Z","msg":"有d想玩，但想PVP既話隻game真係無底深潭黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6de809be38638d0fd3a56fcbbdc69b83f9c5ca61","tid":326551,"uid":57044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T06:23:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有d想玩，但想PVP既話隻game真係無底深潭黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係。又心法又裝又剩，仲難過買樓上車。小弟係休閒派，致在play for fun.<br />\n<br />\nBtw 而家好爆ser，最好晏就入定see<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02a83e3fa61826ec495df3d0fdec11b82f1a3b3b","tid":326551,"uid":10284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T06:25:37.000Z","msg":"上個暑假啱啱出神刀 冇課金都屈死好多人"},{"pid":"516da82a010b3d387d2c41cd869b44f44249bdff","tid":326551,"uid":5372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T06:26:38.000Z","msg":"前排同個台仔fd玩完..一個月後又DEL左GAME<br />\n仲o徒錢買左個咩一飛沖天包..一黎就升到85lv..<br />\n其實隻game 冇fd 一齊玩真係仆街死<br />\n大陸server又唔係好易識到人<br />\n自己走去單機挖寶都周不時有人黎搶<br />\n裝備又要靠打副本黎做..d裝升到2級就停左升唔到上去..<br />\nd副本又難打..野團有d又要上yy..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好多野都夾唔到..如果冇一堆fd一齊玩"},{"pid":"183576ea7b19e252f2d3cc38bbe0b24dc7b9f6ce","tid":326551,"uid":63888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T06:39:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前排同個台仔fd玩完..一個月後又DEL左GAME<br />\n仲o徒錢買左個咩一飛沖天包..一黎就升到85lv..<br />\n其實隻game 冇fd 一齊玩真係仆街死<br />\n大陸server又唔係好易識到人<br />\n自己走去單機挖寶都周不時有人黎搶<br />\n裝備又要靠打副本黎做..d裝升到2級就停左升唔到上去..<br />\nd副本又難打..野團有d又要上yy..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好多野都夾唔到..如果冇一堆fd一齊玩</blockquote><br />\n玩過兩次，兩次都係玩玩下身邊d人棄晒game要上YY同人刷副本我就懶得玩"},{"pid":"f884562ad8899629ffabfac631540e27ff3b68c0","tid":326551,"uid":57044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T07:42:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上個暑假啱啱出神刀 冇課金都屈死好多人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n神刀好型 傅紅雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm